Air Jordan
Air Jordan x Travis Scott Jumpman Jack
£185
Dark Mocha, Black & Sail

Launched on 11/26/2024

Product Launched
After making its initial debut at ComplexCon in Las Vegas, the Jumpman Jack TR Sneaker from Air Jordan x Travis Scott is a blend of functional design wrapped in streetwear-inspired style.

Description

After making its initial debut at ComplexCon in Las Vegas, the Jumpman Jack TR Sneaker from Air Jordan x Travis Scott is a blend of functional design wrapped in streetwear-inspired style. The breathable canvas uppers are overlaid with texturally rich nubuck while the reverse Swoosh appears in smooth suede on the sidewall - a signature of Travis Scott’s design. In terms of branding, you’ll find the iconic Cactus Jack stitched on the heel, a tonal Jumpman on the tongue and a playful oversized ‘Jack’ graphic on the rubber sole.

Features

Breathable Canvas Uppers
Nubuck Overlays
Foam Midsole
Rugged Rubber Outsoles
Lace Up Closure
Tonal Jumpman Logo
Suede Swoosh Branding
Style Code: FZ8117-204
